msgctxt "88_Homeless Guy"
msgid "If anyone can help you, it's Toku-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100_Homeless Guy"
msgid "He's been a Kamurocho local for decades. Spends his time down in the underground mall."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112_Saejima"
msgid "Got a sec? The Sasai Family used to have an office 'round these parts. Know anything 'bout that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124_Homeless Guy"
msgid "Well, I remember some yakuza types used to hang out here,\\r\n"
"but that was, what... 20, 30 years ago?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, those guys. Any idea where their boss went?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148_Homeless Guy"
msgid "Sorry, can't say I do. Toku-san might, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160_Saejima"
msgid "Who's Toku and where do I find him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172_Homeless Guy"
msgid "Another homeless guy like me. He's been busking around town\\r\n"
"for decades. Spends his days down in the <Color:7>underground mall<Color:Default>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184_Saejima"
msgid "The hell's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196_Homeless Guy"
msgid "It's a bunch of stores they set up under Showa Street.\\r\n"
"Built just a while back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208_Homeless Guy"
msgid "The whole thing's one big, fancy shopping center\\r\n"
"beneath the streets. Hence the name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220_Saejima"
msgid "Alright then, guess I'll go see if your pal Toku's still\\r\n"
"hangin' 'round this underground mall."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232_Homeless Guy"
msgid "He should be. And I'm sure he'll be able to tell you\\r\n"
"what you want to know."
msgstr ""

